```json
{
  "application": "MPI",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Python 3",
      "PostgreSQL",
      "mpiexec",
      "deephyper-scalable-bo"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "compute_nodes": 40,
      "walltime": "03:00:00",
      "queue": "prod",
      "account": "datascience",
      "filesystems": ["grand", "home"],
      "environment": "deephyper-scalable-bo",
      "database": {
        "type": "PostgreSQL",
        "authentication": "trust",
        "max_connections": 2048
      }
    },
    "parameters": {
      "problem": "jahs",
      "search": "nsgaii",
      "timeout": 10200,
      "seed": "${PBS_ARRAY_INDEX}",
      "NRANKS_PER_NODE": 4,
      "NDEPTH": 64 / $NRANKS_PER_NODE,
      "NNODES": "Number of nodes specified in PBS_NODEFILE",
      "NTOTRANKS": "NNODES * NRANKS_PER_NODE",
      "OMP_NUM_THREADS": "$NDEPTH",
      "DEEPHYPER_LOG_DIR": "results/$problem-$search-$NNODES-$SEED",
      "OPTUNA_DB_DIR": "$DEEPHYPER_LOG_DIR/optunadb",
      "OPTUNA_DB_HOST": "$HOST"
    }
  }
}
```
